{"tid":1809524,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"妻北角警署候丈夫保釋：他被捕前工作12小時　本欲SOGO買禮物予女兒","createTime":"2020-01-03T07:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T07:35:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ddad5770f3f241ae65a8329243930c7e3b3f5908","tid":1809524,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"40餘歲楊太手持拐杖在警署外等候丈夫保釋，她最擔心丈夫體力透支，丈夫當晚在銅鑼灣附近下班，被捕前已工作逾12小時，「當晚7時半收到他的信息，他說留飯，會先去SOGO（崇光百貨）買新年禮物給女兒」。楊太對丈夫無故被捕感無奈，形容警方行動「難以理解」。她昨晚9時收到警方通知，稱丈夫可保釋，惟至今早仍未能辦理保釋手續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200103/s00001/1578024563505/%e5%a6%bb%e5%8c%97%e8%a7%92%e8%ad%a6%e7%bd%b2%e5%80%99%e4%b8%88%e5%a4%ab%e4%bf%9d%e9%87%8b-%e4%bb%96%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95%e5%89%8d%e5%b7%a5%e4%bd%9c12%e5%b0%8f%e6%99%82-%e6%9c%ac%e6%ac%b2sogo%e8%b2%b7%e7%a6%ae%e7%89%a9%e4%ba%88%e5%a5%b3%e5%85%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200103%2Fs00001%2F1578024563505%2F%25e5%25a6%25bb%25e5%258c%2597%25e8%25a7%2592%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e7%25bd%25b2%25e5%2580%2599%25e4%25b8%2588%25e5%25a4%25ab%25e4%25bf%259d%25e9%2587%258b-%25e4%25bb%2596%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258d%2595%25e5%2589%258d%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e4%25bd%259c12%25e5%25b0%258f%25e6%2599%2582-%25e6%259c%25ac%25e6%25ac%25b2sogo%25e8%25b2%25b7%25e7%25a6%25ae%25e7%2589%25a9%25e4%25ba%2588%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%2585%2592&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7AsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=cbeee493\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200103%2Fs00001%2F1578024563505%2F%25e5%25a6%25bb%25e5%258c%2597%25e8%25a7%2592%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e7%25bd%25b2%25e5%2580%2599%25e4%25b8%2588%25e5%25a4%25ab%25e4%25bf%259d%25e9%2587%258b-%25e4%25bb%2596%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258d%2595%25e5%2589%258d%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e4%25bd%259c12%25e5%25b0%258f%25e6%2599%2582-%25e6%259c%25ac%25e6%25ac%25b2sogo%25e8%25b